---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Person",
  "name": "Stephan Schmied",
  "jobTitle": "Hair & Make-up Artist",
  "description": "Hair & Make-up Artist in Berlin seit 1987. Spezialist für Bridal, Editorial und Events.",
  "url": "https://stephanschmied.com",
  "address": { "@type": "PostalAddress", "addressLocality": "Berlin", "addressCountry": "DE" },
  "sameAs": ["https://instagram.com/schmiedsteph"],
  "knowsAbout": ["Hair Styling", "Make-up Artistry", "Bridal Make-up", "Editorial Make-up"]
};
---

<Layout
  title="Stephan Schmied – Hair & Make-up Artist Berlin"
  description="Hair & Make-up Artist in Berlin seit 1987. Spezialist für Bridal, Editorial, Events und Make-up Coaching. Brand Ambassador Max Factor 2007–2019."
  schemaOrg={schema}
>
  <!-- ═══ HERO ═══ -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner container">
      <div class="hero-photo-col">
        <img
          src="/images/stephan-portrait.jpg"
          alt="Stephan Schmied – Hair & Make-up Artist"
          width="800" height="1000"
          loading="eager"
          fetchpriority="high"
          class="hero-portrait"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="hero-text-col">
        <h1 class="hero-title">STEPHAN SCHMIED</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub1">Hair &amp; Make-up Artist · Berlin</p>
        <p class="hero-sub2">Coaching · Bridal · Editorial</p>
        <div class="hero-buttons">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-anthracite">Coaching buchen</a>
          <a href="/portfolio" class="btn btn-hero-outline">Portfolio</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-scroll-hint" aria-hidden="true">
      <span></span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ LOGO BAR ═══ -->
  <section class="logo-bar">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="logo-strip">VOGUE · ELLE · VANITY FAIR · VICTORIA'S SECRET · GQ · GALA · MAX FACTOR · MERCEDES</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ CELEBRITY INTRO ═══ -->
  <section class="section celeb-intro">
    <div class="container fade-in">
      <div class="celeb-content text-center">
        <span class="label">Von den Covern der Welt zu deinem besonderen Moment</span>
        <h2 class="celeb-headline">VON DEN COVERN DER WELT<br>ZU DEINEM BESONDEREN MOMENT</h2>
        <p class="celeb-credits">KATE MOSS <span class="celeb-dot">·</span> IRIS BERBEN <span class="celeb-dot">·</span> GWYNETH PALTROW <span class="celeb-dot">·</span> LIV TYLER <span class="celeb-dot">·</span> DANIEL BRÜHL <span class="celeb-dot">·</span> HERBERT GRÖNEMEYER <span class="celeb-dot">·</span> FRANZISKA KNUPPE <span class="celeb-dot">·</span> TONI GARN <span class="celeb-dot">·</span> EVA PADBERG <span class="celeb-dot">·</span> SOPHIA THOMALLA <span class="celeb-dot">·</span> KATJA RIEMANN <span class="celeb-dot">·</span> WILSON GONZALEZ OCHSENKNECHT <span class="celeb-dot">·</span> ESTHER SCHWEINS <span class="celeb-dot">·</span> SABRINA SETLUR</p>
        <div class="celeb-text">
          <p>In fast vier Jahrzehnten hatte ich das Privileg, einige der bekanntesten Gesichter der Welt zu stylen – auf Laufstegen, für Kampagnen und auf den Covern internationaler Magazine.</p>
          <p class="mt-sm">Als Hair &amp; Make-up Artist bei Victoria's Secret, als Chef de Cabine für Michalsky, Lala Berlin und Caviar Gauche, und als Brand Ambassador für Max Factor – zwölf Jahre lang.</p>
          <p class="mt-sm">Und jetzt? Jetzt bringe ich genau diese Erfahrung zu dir. Denn du verdienst den gleichen Standard – ob für deine Hochzeit, dein Event oder dein Make-up Coaching. Echte Hände. Echtes Handwerk. Kein Filter.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ ABOUT PREVIEW ═══ -->
  <section class="section about-preview">
    <div class="container about-grid">
      <div class="about-img-wrap fade-in">
        <img
          src="/images/behind-the-scenes/backstage-yacht-styling.jpg"
          alt="Stephan Schmied bei der Arbeit"
          width="600" height="750"
          loading="lazy"
          style="width:100%;aspect-ratio:4/5;object-fit:cover;display:block"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="about-text fade-in delay-1">
        <span class="label">Über mich</span>
        <h2>Fast 40 Jahre<br>Erfahrung</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p>Vom Wiener Friseursalon über internationale Fashion Weeks bis zu den größten Beauty-Magazinen Deutschlands. Mein Talent: die individuelle Schönheit jedes Menschen hervorzuheben.</p>
        <p class="mt-sm">Echte Hände. Echtes Handwerk. In einer Welt voller Filter und KI-generierter Perfektion – ein Artist, der dich wirklich schön macht.</p>
        <a href="/about" class="btn btn-outline mt-md">Mehr über mich</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ SERVICES ═══ -->
  <section class="section services-section" style="background:#fff">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center fade-in">
        <span class="label">Was ich anbiete</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Services</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="services-grid mt-md">
        <a href="/masterclasses" class="service-card fade-in">
          <div class="service-card-img-wrap">
            <img src="/images/behind-the-scenes/backstage-outdoor-lipstick.jpg" alt="Make-up Coaching – Stephan Schmied" width="600" height="400" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="service-card-body">
            <h3>Make-up Coaching</h3>
            <p>Du willst die Techniken lernen, mit denen ich für Vogue und Elle gearbeitet habe? In meinen Coachings zeige ich dir Schritt für Schritt, wie Profis arbeiten – individuell, praxisnah und mit Produkten, die du zu Hause oder bei DM findest.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/services#bridal" class="service-card fade-in delay-1">
          <div class="service-card-img-wrap">
            <img src="/images/portfolio-beauty/bridal-look-01.jpg" alt="Bridal Make-up – Stephan Schmied" width="600" height="400" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="service-card-body">
            <h3>Bridal</h3>
            <p>Dein perfekter Look für den wichtigsten Tag. Vom Probetermin bis zum letzten Tanz.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/services#editorial" class="service-card fade-in delay-2">
          <div class="service-card-img-wrap">
            <img src="/images/portfolio-beauty/beauty-editorial-01.jpg" alt="Editorial & Events – Stephan Schmied" width="600" height="400" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="service-card-body">
            <h3>Editorial &amp; Events</h3>
            <p>Fashion, Beauty, Celebrity. Für Shootings, Kampagnen und Red Carpet.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ TESTIMONIALS ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center fade-in">
        <span class="label">Stimmen meiner Kunden</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Was sie sagen</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonials-grid mt-md">
        <div class="testimonial fade-in">
          <blockquote>"Stephan hat mich an meinem Hochzeitstag so wunderschön gemacht, ich habe mich wie ein Star gefühlt."</blockquote>
          <cite>— Anna K., Braut</cite>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial fade-in delay-1">
          <blockquote>"Professionell, kreativ und unglaublich einfühlsam. Die beste Entscheidung für unser Shooting."</blockquote>
          <cite>— Maria S., Fotografin</cite>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial fade-in delay-2">
          <blockquote>"Nach 40 Jahren Erfahrung merkt man jeden Pinselstrich. Absolute Weltklasse."</blockquote>
          <cite>— Thomas R., Art Director</cite>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ CTA ═══ -->
  <section class="cta-section fade-in">
    <h2>Bereit für deinen Look?</h2>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold">Jetzt Kontakt aufnehmen</a>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* ─── Hero ─── */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: #F5F0EB;
    color: #2C2825;
    display: flex;
    align-items: stretch;
  }
  .hero-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding-top: 80px; /* nav height */
  }
  .hero-photo-col {
    padding: 40px 2rem 40px 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .hero-portrait {
    width: 100%;
    height: calc(100vh - 160px);
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top center;
    display: block;
  }
  .hero-text-col {
    padding: 3rem 3rem 3rem 4rem;
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-signature);
    font-size: 56px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    color: #2C2825;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .hero-sub1 {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(44,40,37,0.65);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    max-width: none;
  }
  .hero-sub2 {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(44,40,37,0.45);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: none;
  }
  .hero-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btn-anthracite {
    background: #2C2825;
    color: #F5F0EB;
    border-color: #2C2825;
  }
  .btn-anthracite:hover {
    background: #A89B8C;
    border-color: #A89B8C;
    color: #F5F0EB;
  }
  .btn-hero-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: #2C2825;
    border: 1px solid #2C2825;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    transition: background var(--transition), color var(--transition);
  }
  .btn-hero-outline:hover {
    background: #2C2825;
    color: #F5F0EB;
  }
  .hero-scroll-hint {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2.5rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .hero-scroll-hint span {
    display: block;
    width: 1px;
    height: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(44,40,37,0.35));
    margin: 0 auto;
    animation: scrollHint 2s ease infinite;
  }
  @keyframes scrollHint {
    0%   { transform: scaleY(0); transform-origin: top; }
    50%  { transform: scaleY(1); transform-origin: top; }
    51%  { transform: scaleY(1); transform-origin: bottom; }
    100% { transform: scaleY(0); transform-origin: bottom; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      min-height: auto;
      padding-top: 70px;
    }
    .hero-photo-col {
      padding: 24px 1.5rem 0;
    }
    .hero-portrait {
      height: auto;
      max-height: 60vw;
      min-height: 260px;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .hero-text-col {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem 3rem;
    }
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 40px;
      white-space: normal;
    }
    .hero-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }

  /* ─── Celebrity Intro ─── */
  .celeb-intro { background: var(--color-bg); }
  .celeb-content.text-center { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .celeb-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.5vw, 1.6rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: #2C2825;
    margin: 0.75rem 0 2rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .celeb-credits {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', var(--font-heading), sans-serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #2C2825;
    line-height: 2;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }
  .celeb-dot {
    color: #A89B8C;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .celeb-credits { font-size: 18px; }
  }
  .celeb-text p {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ─── About preview ─── */
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .about-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    background: #D5CFC8;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .about-placeholder span {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(44,40,37,0.45);
  }
  .about-text h2 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem); }

  /* ─── Services ─── */
  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .service-card {
    display: block;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: box-shadow var(--transition);
  }
  .service-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
  .service-card-img-wrap { overflow: hidden; }
  .service-card img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.45s ease;
  }
  .service-card:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }
  .service-card-body { padding: 1.5rem; }
  .service-card-body h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .service-card-body p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    max-width: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--sp-md); }
    .about-placeholder { max-width: 360px; }
  }

</style>
